This project is intended to suppor my blog post.
Post link: http://migre.me/DUiE

Use mvn scala:console to play importint CEP and CEP._

CEP.start function: returns a Drools session, a Stream and a pseudoclock instance. This is de method used in Test scripts.
CEP.MyTimer.advanceSeconds advance the session timer and return a timestamp to be used in the new event.


